Former Gartmore Managers Guy, Rambourg Plan Fund, Times Reports

-- B y   R a c h e l   G r a h a m
-- 
2011-04-10T13:43:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-10/former-gartmore-managers-guy-rambourg-plan-fund-times-reports.html
Roger Guy and Guillaume Rambourg,
former fund managers at  Gartmore Group Ltd. (GRT) , plan to set up a
hedge fund, the Sunday Times reported, without saying where it
got the information.  The fund would be based in London, Paris or Geneva, the
report said. Gartmore is now owned by  Henderson Group Plc. (HGG)   To contact the reporter on this story:
Rachel Graham in London at 
 rgraham13@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Harrison at 
 mharrison5@bloomberg.net . 